column2: plots[[i]] <- ggplot(data = df[df$B11month == month,]) + geom_point(aes(x=B11dif, y = THD1), color = "dodgerblue", alpha = 0.2) + facet_wrap(~B11) +    ggtitle(month) + xlab("Time elasped in seconds") + ylab("THD1") + theme_bw() + theme(panel.border = element_blank(), panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(), axis.ticks.x=element_blank(), axis.ticks.y=element_blank(), plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5), axis.line = element_line(colour = "black"))
grid.arrange(plots[[2]], plots[[3]], plots[[4]], plots[[5]], plots[[6]], plots[[7]], ncol=2, top = "Filter B11")
